headline: The Hershey Company Rolls Out an Egg-cellent Easter Collection Fans Will Love
summary: The Hershey Company is hopping into Easter with an exciting new offering, Jolly Rancher Gummies Fruity Mix plus an expanded mix of returning fan-favorites, including Hershey's Kisses Harry Potter Butterbeer Flavor, Cadbury Mini Creme Egg, Cadbury Mini Caramel Egg, and Reese's Peanut Butter Mini Eggs Unwrapped.
